title: Discography Jose Beausejour 2013 [Metal]
description:
"Un supplice pire que la paille de verre"
"Jose Beausejour has a refreshing approach to remixing music. He takes tracks from sources such as Notorious BIG and Ennio Morricone and applies his own unique style to present them in a way that the original producers could not imagine.Do not think that he is just adding a bass line and some new mid-range beats. Consider if you will a haunting melody being played by the likes of Sepultura but with the original artists vocals. If you thought that Metallica's cover of 'Ecstasy of Gold' was good then you really need to hear his take on this track. Simply brilliant"
